2014-12-19  kstn  <kastian@mail.ru>

	FIX FightMode.sh
	To prevent screen blinking in console and old terms (xterm for
	instance) now we do not call GX_Monster every time, but:

	Call GX_Monster "$ENEMY" first time
	Store cursor position (tput sc)
	And then (when we need it) just restore cursor position (tput rc) and
	clear all from this position to the end of screen (tput ed)

