2014-10-15  kstn  <kastian@mail.ru>

	FIX Makefile
	Bash can be located in diffirent places. For instance in OpenBSD it
	located in /usr/local/bin/bash. So

	SHABANG = `which bash`

	defines where bash is located, and

	        @echo "#!${SHABANG}" > ${NAME}

	add right sha-bang for current system.

