	HowTo split some functions from functions.sh

	1. Cut needed code from functions.sh

	2. Paste it to 'newfile.sh'

	3. add 'newfile.sh' to Makefile in line FILES = FightMode.sh functions.sh newfile.sh

	4. run

	$ make

