2014-08-23  kstn  <kastian@mail.ru>

	REWRITTEN Calendar system
	I'm sorry if I've break smth in Almanac(), but this system is really
	easier and all calendar variables are global (loads only once at
	start) and in one place - easily to change

	They should be used through functions like -

	echo "$(MonthString 1)"        -> "After-Frost"
	echo "$(MonthLength 1)"        -> "31"
	echo "$(MonthTrivia 1)"        -> "1st Month of the Year\n This is the coldest and darkest month of the year. Stay in, stay warm."
	echo "$(WeekdayString 1)"      -> "Ringday (Holiday)"
	echo "$(WeekdayTriviaShort 1)" -> "Day of Festivities and Rest"
	echo "$(WeekdayTriviaLong 1)"  -> "Men and Halflings celebrate Ringday as the end and beginning of the week."

